General.Name: Judo Capital Holdings Ltd
General.Description: Judo Capital Holdings Limited provides various banking products and services for small and medium businesses in Australia. It accepts term deposits; and provides business loans, lines of credit, home loans, residential mortgages, asset financing, equipment loan, and bank guarantees, as well as agribusiness. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Melbourne, Australia.
